# Trivy CVE exceptions. Each line corresponds to an RG-SEC-XXX entry
# in SECURITY_EXCEPTIONS.md. Format:
#   CVE-ID exp:YYYY-MM-DD  # short note (RG-SEC-XXX)
#
# Expiry policy: revisit on next base-image bump or every 6 months,
# whichever comes first.

